 expected results. I believe assertions will be helpful here, but I need to confirm all elements are in place.\"},{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Evaluating CPU load values**\\n\\nI’m contemplating how CpuLoad might start as -1, and its value should range between -1.0 and 1.0. The `getProcessCpuLoad` function should return a double in [0,1] unless it’s unavailable, which could lead to a negative value. I could assert that it’s not NaN upon success. There’s possibility for negative values under HotSpot, and for a native image, it might return 0. I’ll check tags and ensure my Java test file is set up correctly.\"}]}"}, {"type": "toolCall", "id": "call_bCnd9ETaGXlrY6NBLkQjhODa|fc_0cea65e695715eff0169f11dd94cd881919e46f390ca91a05f", "name": "bash", "arguments": {"command": "git status --short", "timeout": 10}}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 964, "output": 761, "cacheRead": 14848, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 16573, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "toolUse", "timestamp": 1777409482606, "responseId": "resp_0cea65e695715eff0169f11dcb0ff08191960e943703e685dd"}}
